item.title: What is router
item.dc:creator: @93dcthugs93 93dcthugs93
item.description:
@93dcthugs93 wrote:

A router is something that connects two or more computers in a network.

Basically, it gives the other computers access to the internet. If you don’t have one, it’s a good thing if you want to use no-ip.
